modName: Malukah Age of Aggression main menu theme replacer
summary: This mod replaces the intro song with a cut version of Malukah's "Age of Aggression" cover. i cut it down, it would start sooner cause most people just spam enter on the continue page :)
descriptionHtml:
This mod replaces the intro song with a cut version of Malukah's "Age of Aggression" cover. i cut it down, it would start sooner cause most people just spam enter on the continue page :)
so what are you waiting for!!!!

thanks to Malukah for letting me use her awesome song. and thanks also for being awesome and making awesome stuff in the first place.
thanks Bethesda for making a pretty good game and then allowing it to be modded to become the best game of all time.

installation: just drop the data file in Skyrim's default path.

apologies if the audio is a little quiet
author: Any Time Other Than Friday
